        "content": "<p>We've always said that we have a translation extension for language translation</p>",
        "id": 153839951,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1468995011
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>but I've just gone to use, and discovered that it's... useless</p>",
        "id": 153839952,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1468995029
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre>&lt;extension xmlns=&quot;http://hl7.org/fhir&quot; url=&quot;http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/iso21090-ST-translation&quot; &gt;\n   &lt;valueString value=&quot;rwefwf&quot;/&gt;\n&lt;/extension&gt;\n</pre></div>",
        "id": 153839953,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1468995060
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>where's the language.... </p>",
        "id": 153839954,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1468995066
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>grrr</p>",
        "id": 153839955,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1468995068
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>has anyone used this or another approach for real? how did you do it? </p>",
        "id": 153839956,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1468995081
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Language is a second extension - which can appear on the translation or on the base string.</p>",
        "id": 153839991,
        "sender_full_name": "Lloyd McKenzie",
        "timestamp": 1469022101
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Probably would be good to declare that extension is mandatory on the translation extension though . . .</p>",
        "id": 153839993,
        "sender_full_name": "Lloyd McKenzie",
        "timestamp": 1469022134
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>actually, it turned out I was already making extensive use of another extension, so I defined it properly</p>",
        "id": 153840089,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1469052087
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre>&lt;extension url=&quot;http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/translation&quot; &gt;\n   &lt;extension url=&quot;lang&quot;&gt;\n     &lt;valueCode value=&quot;de&quot;/&gt;\n   &lt;/extension&gt;\n   &lt;extension url=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;valueString value=&quot;rwefwf&quot;/&gt;\n   &lt;/extension&gt;\n&lt;/extension&gt;\n</pre></div>",
        "id": 153840092,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1469052215
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Um, why use that one instead of the 21090 ones that do the same thing?</p>",
        "id": 153840142,
        "sender_full_name": "Lloyd McKenzie",
        "timestamp": 1469067344
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>it's poxy. I'll retire the iso 21090 extensions and map this one instead</p>",
